urses, from description, content, purposes of the courses, number of students can enroll to the courses, teachers and tutors, number of lessons and quizzes, requirement to enroll the courses&#8230; </p>\n<h3 id=\"item-description__event-management\">Event Management</h3>\n<p> Ivy School Theme also include the event management which helps you easily share events on your website. The section contains a list of upcoming events of the university. Besides, a features event will be shown off with a countdown clock. You can create and manage events on your website efficiently. With event manager, you will make sure that your customers will never miss out amazing events. Furthermore, you can sell event tickets in your website via built-in online ticket booking form. The users will find it easy to fill in the form and discover how many slots are already taken and how many slots left of each event. \n</p><h2 id=\"item-description__-premium-plugins-coming-with-theme-package\"> Premium Plugins for School coming with Theme package </h2>\n<h3 id=\"item-description__learnpress-and-bundle-of-learnpress-premium-add-ons\">LearnPress and Bundle of LearnPress Premium add-ons: </h3> <p>Besides LearnPress free plugin, Ivy School WordPress Theme comes with Bundle of Premium add-ons supporting more functions and features for the LearnPress plugin. With the bundle, we extremely proudly confirm that this university WordPress theme is the #1 theme for school, university, academy and any educational institution. So, do not worry about loading of the bundle, you can easily deactive or active any add-on as per your request. </p>\n<h2 id=\"item-description__-flexible-payment-option\">Flexible Course &#38; Program Payment Option</h2>\n <p>With Ivy School WordPress Theme, it&#8217;s your choice to select a payment methods for your website. You can choose with this university WordPress theme any among the options: WooCommerce, Paypal, Stripe, 2Checkout and Authorize.net. Besides selling courses indi