ail settings.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-7.png?rev=2591302\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-7.png?rev=2591302\" alt=\"Demo course page.\"></a><p>Demo course page.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-8.png?rev=2591302\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-8.png?rev=2591302\" alt=\"Add-ons of LearnPress.\"></a><p>Add-ons of LearnPress.</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:16799:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Not usable right out of the box</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jwrhodes2008/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2fb36352179cdf9a6b5f39a2021143a9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2fb36352179cdf9a6b5f39a2021143a9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jwrhodes2008/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jwrhodes2008</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 7, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I would have given this a much higher rating in the past. But now, the new plug in requires a lot, I mean LOT of work on the back end. Unless you plan on buying their extremely limited capability themes, this plug in does not play well with many other themes out there unless you are planning to put in a lot of work coding your own CSS and PHP. \n\nTheir support is ok, but I often get \"What you requested can\'t be done\" or in my most recent experience their support team claimed they could not access my site, when the screenshot they sent me clearly showed their browser was not configured correctly for WP. If their support can\'t figure out how to use the browser correctly, I have very little hope they can fix a problem their plugin is causing. \n\nI often have to go in and code things myself to get templates to work as they were originally described. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great free LMS for Offering Online Courses</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aabharali/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/21ba7ae9998b02c8a37b312e732ffbd8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/21ba7ae9998b02c8a37b312e732ffbd8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aabharali/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">aabharali</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 15, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Have been using it for almost a year now. Installation was simple. Finding it quite user-friendly and easy to work with. Convenient interface to create courses, lessons, quizzes etc. Highly recommended! </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Support Team!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/adw259/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/27437933e2ed89dab8321e3b1d7dd066?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/27437933e2ed89dab8321e3b1d7dd066?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/adw259/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">adw259</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 7, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">These guys offer great support. I am very impressed about how quickly and willing they are to support LesrnPress and their add-ons.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">it&#039;s not so good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out o