(122, 1, '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-contact-teacher -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-contact-teacher is-style-outline wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\">Contact Teacher</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-contact-teacher -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Registered users have the ability to send a private message to teachers, regardless of whether or not they are enrolled in a particular course. This allows enrolled learners to ask questions about course materials, while also enabling those who are not enrolled to get answers to their general course questions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All messages are private and can only be viewed by the teacher, the sender, and site administrators.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Send a Message</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To send a private message to the course teacher, click the <em>Contact Teacher</em> button on the course, lesson or quiz page. This button is only displayed when logged in:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":5211,\"width\":735,\"height\":230,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/messages-contact-teacher.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Messages - Contact Teacher\" class=\"wp-image-5211\" width=\"735\" height=\"230\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After clicking the button, a text field appears to enter the message:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":5213,\"width\":735,\"height\":169,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/messages-send-message.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Messages - Send Private Message\" class=\"wp-image-5213\" width=\"735\" height=\"169\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once the message is sent, a confirmation notice is displayed:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3531,\"width\":735,\"height\":80,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/messages-message-sent.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Messages - Confirmation\" class=\"wp-image-3531\" width=\"735\" height=\"80\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Depending on how notifications are configured in <em>Sensei LMS</em> &gt; <em>Settings</em> &gt; <em>Email Notifications</em>, an email may be sent to the teacher to let them know that they have received a new message.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>View a Message</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a teacher, you can view your messages by going to <em>Sensei LMS</em> &gt; <em>Messages</em>, hovering over the message, and clicking the <em>View</em> link.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As an administrator, in <em>Sensei LMS</em> &gt; <em>Messages</em> you can click on a message to view additional details:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3535,\"width\":735,\"height\":156,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/messages-message-information.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Messages - Message Information\" class=\"wp-image-3535\" width=\"735\" height=\"156\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Reply to a Message</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The easiest way to reply to a message is by visiting the <em>My Courses</em> page and clicking on <em>My Messages</em>. A list of all the messages you\'ve received are displayed:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":5215,\"width\":735,\"height\":282,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/my-messages.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Messages - My Messages\" class=\"wp-image-5215\" width=\"735\" height=\"282\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Click on the message you\'d like to reply to, and type your response in the text field:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":5217,\"width\":735,\"height\":407,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/messages-reply.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Messages - Leave a Reply\" class=\"wp-image-5217\" width=\"735\" height=\"407\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Depending on how notifications are configured in <em>Sensei LMS</em> &gt; <em>Settings</em> &gt; <em>Email Notifications</em>, an email may be sent to the learner to let them know they have received a reply to their message.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>My Messages</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Teachers and learners can access their messages by going to <em>My Courses</em> and clicking the <em>My Messages</em> button. You can also add a direct link to the <em>My Messages</em> page in your main menu by going to <em>Appearance</em> &gt; <em>Menus</em>, and adding a custom link that goes to <code>https://yoursite.com/messages/</code> (be sure to change <code>yoursite.com</code> to your own domain).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Disable Private Messages</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Private messages are enabled by default. To disable them, go to <em>Sensei LMS</em> &gt; <em>Settings</em> and check the <em>Disable Private Messages</em> box. This removes the <em>My Messages</em> page, the <em>Contact Teacher</em> buttons, and the <em>Sensei LMS</em> &gt; <em>Messages</em> menu in WordPress admin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/lesson-actions -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-lesson-actions\"><div class=\"sensei-buttons-container\"><!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-view-quiz {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-view-quiz is-style-default sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-view-quiz__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-view-quiz is-style-default wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link\">View Quiz</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-view-quiz -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-complete-lesson {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-complete-lesson is-style-default sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-complete-lesson__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-complete-lesson is-style-default wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link sensei-stop-double-submission\">Complete Lesson</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-complete-lesson -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-next-lesson {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-next-lesson is-style-default sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-next-lesson__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-next-lesson is-style-default wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link\">Next Lesson</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-next-lesson -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-reset-lesson {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-reset-lesson is-style-outline sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-reset-lesson__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-reset-lesson is-style-outline wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link sensei-stop-double-submission\">Reset Lesson</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-reset-lesson --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/lesson-actions -->', 'Messages', 'Learn how to manage messages from learners in Sensei LMS.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'messages', '', '', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/lesson/messages/', 0, 'lesson', '', 0),
