(126, 1, '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-contact-teacher -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-contact-teacher is-style-outline wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\">Contact Teacher</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-contact-teacher -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Learner Management enables you to manage everything about your learners, from enrolling new learners to resetting their progress.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Go to <em>Sensei LMS</em> &gt; <em>Learner Management</em>&nbsp;to see a list of courses. You can filter by course category or search for a particular course:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3336,\"width\":735,\"height\":194,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/learner-management.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Learner Management\" class=\"wp-image-3336\" width=\"735\" height=\"194\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>From here, learners can be managed by <a href=\"#manage-learners-course\">course</a> or by <a href=\"#manage-learners-lesson\">lesson</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 id=\"manage-learners-course\">Manage Learners By Course</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To manage your learners, locate the relevant course and click the <em>Manage learners</em> button. By default, a list of all learners who were ever enrolled in the course are displayed. This view can be filtered to only show those learners who are currently enrolled (<em>Enrolled Learners</em>), or only those who are unenrolled (<em>Unenrolled Learners</em>):</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3649,\"width\":735,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/learner-management-all-learners.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Learner Management - Manage learners\" class=\"wp-image-3649\" width=\"735\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Remove a Learner from a Course</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To remove a learner\'s enrollment in a course, find the appropriate learner and hover over their name. Click the&nbsp;<em>Remove Enrollment</em>&nbsp;link that appears. This will unenroll the learner and revoke their access to the course:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3627,\"width\":735,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/remove-enrollment.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Learner Management - Remove Enrollment\" class=\"wp-image-3627\" width=\"735\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please note that while the learner no longer has access to the course, their progress is preserved. This means that they will be able to pick up where they left off should they enroll in the course again later.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Add a Learner to a Course</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If a learner already appears in Learner Management, but are not currently enrolled in the course, they can be re-enrolled by hovering over their name and clicking the <em>Enroll</em> link:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3629,\"width\":735,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/enroll.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Learner Management - Enroll\" class=\"wp-image-3629\" width=\"735\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If a learner does not already appear in Learner Management, they can be added by scrolling to the bottom of the page, searching for and selecting them in the <em>Add Learner to Course</em> panel, and clicking the button. You can optionally choose to complete the course for the learner by checking the <em>Complete course for learner</em> box. Multiple learners can be added simultaneously:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3375,\"width\":735,\"height\":320,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/learner-management-add-learner.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Learner Management - Add learner to course\" class=\"wp-image-3375\" width=\"735\" height=\"320\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Reset Progress</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To reset a learner\'s progress and have them start the course over from the beginning, find the learner, hover over their name, and click the <em>Reset Progress</em> link. This will reset the course start date and set its status to <em>In Progress</em>. All lessons in the course will have their start date cleared and status set to <em>Not started</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Note that the <em>Reset Progress</em> link is only displayed if the learner is currently enrolled in the course.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Remove Progress</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To remove a learner\'s progress, find the learner, hover over their name, and click the <em>Remove Progress</em> link. This will remove the learner from Learner Management, effectively deleting any progress they have already made in the course. This means the learner will need to start the course over from the beginning should they enroll again later.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Note that the <em>Remove Progress</em> link is only displayed if the learner is <strong>not</strong> currently enrolled in the course.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Edit the Course Start Date</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can edit the course start date by locating the learner, clicking in the text box that displays the current start date, selecting a new date from the calendar that appears, and clicking the <em>Edit Start Date</em> button.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Note that updating the course start date does not have any effect on the start dates of the course\'s lessons.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 id=\"manage-learners-lesson\">Manage Learners by Lesson</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Clicking the <em>Lessons</em> link displays a list of all lessons in the course:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3354,\"width\":735,\"height\":222,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/learner-management-lessons.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Learner Management - Lessons\" class=\"wp-image-3354\" width=\"735\" height=\"222\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As with courses, the learners for an individual lesson can be managed by clicking the <em>Manage learners</em> button. By default, a list of all learners who ever viewed the lesson are displayed:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3656,\"width\":735,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/learner-management-lessons-all-learners.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Learner Management - Manage learners by lesson\" class=\"wp-image-3656\" width=\"735\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Add a Learner to a Lesson</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A learner can be added to the lesson by scrolling to the bottom of the page, searching for and selecting them in the <em>Add Learner to Lesson</em> panel, and clicking the button. This will also enroll the learner in the course if they are not already taking it. You can optionally choose to complete the lesson for the learner by checking the <em>Complete lesson for learner</em> box. If the lesson has a quiz, the learner will automatically pass it. Multiple learners can be added simultaneously:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3373,\"width\":735,\"height\":306,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/learner-management-lesson-add-learner.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Learner Management - Add learner to lesson\" class=\"wp-image-3373\" width=\"735\" height=\"306\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Reset Progress</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To reset a learner\'s progress and have them start the lesson over from the beginning, find the learner, hover over their name, and click the <em>Reset Progress</em> link. This will reset the lesson status to <em>In Progress</em>. If the lesson has a quiz, this will also reset the learner\'s grade for that quiz and remove their answers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Edit the Lesson Start Date</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can edit the lesson start date by locating the learner, clicking in the text box that displays the current start date, selecting a new date from the calendar that appears, and clicking the <em>Edit Start Date</em> button.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/lesson-actions -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-lesson-actions\"><div class=\"sensei-buttons-container\"><!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-view-quiz {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-view-quiz is-style-default sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-view-quiz__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-view-quiz is-style-default wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link\">View Quiz</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-view-quiz -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-complete-lesson {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-complete-lesson is-style-default sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-complete-lesson__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-complete-lesson is-style-default wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link sensei-stop-double-submission\">Complete Lesson</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-complete-lesson -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-next-lesson {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-next-lesson is-style-default sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-next-lesson__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-next-lesson is-style-default wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link\">Next Lesson</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-next-lesson -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-reset-lesson {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-reset-lesson is-style-outline sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-reset-lesson__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-reset-lesson is-style-outline wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link sensei-stop-double-submission\">Reset Lesson</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-reset-lesson --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/lesson-actions -->', 'Learner Management', 'Learn how to manage your learners in Sensei LMS.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'learner-management', '', '', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/lesson/learner-management/', 0, 'lesson', '', 0),
(127, 1, '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '', 'Learner Management', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'learner-management', '', '', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '', 126, 'http://localhost/wordpress/quiz/learner-management/', 0, 'quiz', '', 0),
(128, 1, '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-contact-teacher -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-contact-teacher is-style-outline wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\">Contact Teacher</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-contact-teacher -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sensei LMS offers drill-down reporting for you to see how learners are progressing across all courses, lessons and quizzes. To access this area, go to&nbsp;<em>Sensei LMS</em> &gt; <em>Analysis</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are three main areas in this section:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><a href=\"#learners\">Learners</a></li><li><a href=\"#courses\">Courses</a></li><li><a href=\"#lessons\">Lessons</a></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 id=\"learners\">Learners</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The default view of the <em>Analysis</em> page shows an overview of your learners and their stats, all of which can be exported:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><em>Learner</em> - Learner\'s username</li><li><em>Email</em> - Learner\'s email address</li><li><em>Date Registered</em> - Date on which the learner registered on your site</li><li><em>Active Courses</em> - Number of courses the learner is currently enrolled in</li><li><em>Completed Courses</em> - Number of courses the learner has completed</li><li><em>Average Grade</em> - Learner\'s average grade across all courses</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3239,\"width\":735,\"height\":339,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/analysis-learners.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Analysis - Learners\" class=\"wp-image-3239\" width=\"735\" height=\"339\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drilling down into a particular learner displays a page that lists the following information:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><em>Course</em> - Name of the course</li><li><em>Date Started</em> - Date on which the learner started the course</li><li><em>Date Completed</em> - Date on which the learner completed the course</li><li><em>Status</em> - Course status</li><li><em>Percent Complete</em> - Percentage of the course the learner has completed so far</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3244,\"width\":734,\"height\":186,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/learner-courses.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Analysis - Learner courses\" class=\"wp-image-3244\" width=\"734\" height=\"186\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drilling down even further into a specific course displays the learner\'s progress at the lesson level:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><em>Lesson</em> - Name of the lesson</li><li><em>Date Started</em> - Date on which the learner started the lesson</li><li><em>Date Completed</em> - Date on which the learner completed the lesson</li><li><em>Status</em> - Lesson status</li><li><em>Grade</em> - Learner\'s grade for that lesson, if applicable</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3246,\"width\":735,\"height\":257,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/learner-course-lessons.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Analysis - Learner course lessons\" class=\"wp-image-3246\" width=\"735\" height=\"257\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><p id=\"course-learners\">The <em>Other Learners taking this Course</em> view shows all other learners currently enrolled in the course:</p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3249,\"width\":735,\"height\":240,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/course-learners.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Analysis - Course learners\" class=\"wp-image-3249\" width=\"735\" height=\"240\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 id=\"courses\">Courses</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Similar to&nbsp;the <em>Learners</em> view, the <em>Courses</em> view displays an overview of your courses with some stats, all of which can be exported:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><em>Course</em> - Name of the course</li><li><em>Learners</em> - Number of learners currently enrolled in the course</li><li><em>Lessons</em> - Number of lessons in the course</li><li><em>Completed</em> - Number of learners who have completed the course</li><li><em>Average Percentage</em> - Average percentage of the course across all learners</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3224,\"width\":735,\"height\":290,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/analysis-courses.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Analysis - Courses\" class=\"wp-image-3224\" width=\"735\" height=\"290\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drilling down into a particular course displays a page that lists all of the lessons in the course, as well as the following stats:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><em>Learners</em> - Number of learners who are currently taking or have already completed the lesson</li><li><em>Completed</em> - Number of learners who have completed the lesson</li><li><em>Average Grade</em> - Average grade of the lesson, if applicable</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3228,\"width\":735,\"height\":246,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/course-lessons.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Analysis - Course lessons\" class=\"wp-image-3228\" width=\"735\" height=\"246\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The<em> Learners taking this Course</em> view shows all other learners currently enrolled in the course. The view is identical to <a href=\"#course-learners\">this one</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<p id=\"course-lesson-learners\">Drilling down even further into a specific lesson displays all learners who are currently taking or have already completed the lesson:</p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3234,\"width\":734,\"height\":194,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/course-lesson-learners.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Analysis - Course lesson learners\" class=\"wp-image-3234\" width=\"734\" height=\"194\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 id=\"lessons\">Lessons</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Much like the <em>Learners</em> and <em>Courses</em> views, the <em>Lessons</em> view displays an overview of your lessons with some stats, all of which can be exported:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><em>Lesson</em> - Name of the lesson</li><li><em>Module</em> - Name of the module the lesson is in</li><li><em>Course</em> - Name of the course the lesson is in</li><li><em>Learners</em> - Number of learners who are currently taking or have already completed the lesson</li><li><em>Completed</em> - Number of learners who have completed the lesson</li><li><em>Average Grade</em> - Average grade of the lesson, if applicable</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3252,\"width\":735,\"height\":198,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/analysis-lessons.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Analysis - Lessons\" class=\"wp-image-3252\" width=\"735\" height=\"198\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drilling down into a particular lesson displays a page that lists all of the learners who are currently taking or have already completed the lesson. The view is the same as <a href=\"#course-lesson-learners\">this one</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/lesson-actions -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-lesson-actions\"><div class=\"sensei-buttons-container\"><!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-view-quiz {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-view-quiz is-style-default sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-view-quiz__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-view-quiz is-style-default wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link\">View Quiz</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-view-quiz -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-complete-lesson {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-complete-lesson is-style-default sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-complete-lesson__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-complete-lesson is-style-default wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link sensei-stop-double-submission\">Complete Lesson</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-complete-lesson -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-next-lesson {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-next-lesson is-style-default sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-next-lesson__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-next-lesson is-style-default wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link\">Next Lesson</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-next-lesson -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-reset-lesson {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-reset-lesson is-style-outline sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-reset-lesson__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-reset-lesson is-style-outline wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link sensei-stop-double-submission\">Reset Lesson</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-reset-lesson --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/lesson-actions -->', 'Analysis', 'Learn how to track your learners\' course progress in Sensei LMS.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'analysis', '', '', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/lesson/analysis/', 0, 'lesson', '', 0),
