(132, 1, '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-contact-teacher -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-contact-teacher is-style-outline wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\">Contact Teacher</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-contact-teacher -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sensei LMS enables teachers to manually grade a lesson. To access this area, go to&nbsp;<em>Sensei LMS</em> &gt; <em>Grading</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By default, the <em>Grading</em> page lists all of the ungraded quizzes that have been submitted for manual grading. The following columns are displayed:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><em>Learner</em> - Name of the learner</li><li><em>Course</em> - Name of the course</li><li><em>Lesson</em> - Name of the lesson</li><li><em>Updated</em> - Date and time the learner last viewed or interacted with the quiz</li><li><em>Status</em> - Grading status (<em>Ungraded</em>, <em>Graded</em>, <em>In Progress</em>)</li><li><em>Grade</em> - Learner\'s grade for the quiz or <em>N/A</em> if not yet graded</li><li>Button for grading the quiz or reviewing an existing grade</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3275,\"width\":735,\"height\":244,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/grading.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Grading\" class=\"wp-image-3275\" width=\"735\" height=\"244\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Filter the Quizzes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The table can be filtered to only show quizzes for a particular lesson by selecting a course and then a lesson from the drop-downs. To remove lesson filtering, click the <em>Reset filter</em> button.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The view can also be changed such that all quizzes are displayed, or only those that are ungraded, graded, or in progress:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3278,\"width\":735,\"height\":205,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/quiz-filter-by-lesson.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Grading - Filtered\" class=\"wp-image-3278\" width=\"735\" height=\"205\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To show quizzes for a specific learner, enter the learner into the search box and click the <em>Search Users</em> button. To display all learners again, clear the search box and submit an empty search:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3280,\"width\":735,\"height\":221,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/quiz-search-by-learner.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Grading - Search by learner\" class=\"wp-image-3280\" width=\"735\" height=\"221\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Grade a Quiz</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To grade a quiz, locate the quiz in the table and click the <em>Grade quiz</em> button. If the quiz has already been graded, the button will be named <em>Review grade</em> instead:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3292,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/grade-quiz.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Grading - Grade quiz\" class=\"wp-image-3292\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Any questions that were auto-graded at the time the quiz was submitted will already be marked. The remaining questions can be manually graded by clicking the checkmark or X icons.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For each question, you can also:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Add grading notes. Use these to provide feedback to learners about their answer.</li><li>Assign a specific grade to an answer. This value must not exceed the question\'s original grade.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When a learner views their graded quiz, they will see which questions they got right, as well as their grade for each question and their total grade for the entire quiz. They will also be able to see any grading notes that were entered by the teacher:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":3294,\"width\":735,\"height\":576,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://senseilms.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/learner-graded-quiz.jpg?w=980\" alt=\"Graded quiz\" class=\"wp-image-3294\" width=\"735\" height=\"576\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/lesson-actions -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-lesson-actions\"><div class=\"sensei-buttons-container\"><!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-view-quiz {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-view-quiz is-style-default sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-view-quiz__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-view-quiz is-style-default wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link\">View Quiz</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-view-quiz -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-complete-lesson {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-complete-lesson is-style-default sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-complete-lesson__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-complete-lesson is-style-default wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link sensei-stop-double-submission\">Complete Lesson</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-complete-lesson -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-next-lesson {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-next-lesson is-style-default sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-next-lesson__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-next-lesson is-style-default wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link\">Next Lesson</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-next-lesson -->\n\n<!-- wp:sensei-lms/button-reset-lesson {\"inContainer\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-reset-lesson is-style-outline sensei-buttons-container__button-block wp-block-sensei-lms-button-reset-lesson__wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-sensei-lms-button-reset-lesson is-style-outline wp-block-sensei-button wp-block-button has-text-align-left\"><button class=\"wp-block-button__link sensei-stop-double-submission\">Reset Lesson</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/button-reset-lesson --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:sensei-lms/lesson-actions -->', 'Grading', 'Learn how to grade quizzes in Sensei LMS.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'grading', '', '', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '2021-12-23 21:09:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/lesson/grading/', 0, 'lesson', '', 0);
